==English==
===Transitive verb===
'''to ridicule''' (ridiculed, ridiculing, ridicules)
# to make [[fun]] of someone

====Translations====
*Estonian: [[naeruvääristama]], [[pilkama]]
*Finnish: [[asettaa naurunalaiseksi]], [[ivata]]
*Romanian: [[a batjocori]], [[a ridiculiza]]

===Noun===
'''ridicule'''
# [[derision]]; [[mocking]] or [[humiliating]] words or behaviour


Though the word humiliate in US society is often considered a much more offensive action.

